\id ZEP  
\h Zephaniah 
\toc1 Zephaniah Themgao Lekhabu 
\toc2 Zephaniah 
\toc3 Zephaniah 
\mt1 ZEPHANIAH  
\mt2 THEMGAO LEKHABU  
\mt3 Zephaniah Themgao Lekhabu Sung Thu Umdan  
\ip Hiche phatlai chun, Judah gamsung umdan chu koima Pathen ging’a, Thudih leh Thutah’a Pathen hou ana umlou ahi. Gamsung pumpia mipiten jong, thudih leh alhem ahekhen thei pouvin, Thudih in mun anei jou pon, Thempu ho jengin jong Pathen thutah hol louvin, in’ah milim doi houna maicham aphalpeh un, Pathen muntheng jouse asuboh gam’un ahi.  
\ip Hitobang lah a chun, Josiah lengpan ajochan in, Pathen dihtah chu, thudihtah’a houna ding angaiton, alenggam sung pumpi semphatna aneiyin, Pathen lunglam ahol’e. Ahivangin miho lungsung chu setnan alo dim in, akikhel dehpon, Pathen dei hol’a aum pouvin ahi.  
\ip Hijeh chun Pathen'in, Zephaniah henga thu ahinseija, Judah mite chunga alunghanna thutanna ahunglhun ding thudol ahilchen sah ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu Jihpa Chule Akijih Kum  
\ip Hiche lekhabu hi, Cushi chapa Zephaniah jih ahi. Ama phatlai chun, Judah gamsung’a Josiah in lengvai anapon, hichu 640-609 BC sung ahi. Zephaniah min hi, “Pathen'in avenbit ahilouleh Pathen'in asel,” tina ahi. Ama toh khang kibang anaum themgao ho chu, Jeremiah leh Nahum ahilhon’e. Ajihna phat hi, 630-627 BC sung ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Pakai Thutanna Le Lungsatna  
\p
\v 1 Amon chapa Josiah in Judah gam’a lengvai apohlaijin, Pakaiyin hiche thu hi Zephaniah kitipa heng’a ahin sei tai. Zephaniah chu Cushi chapa, Cushi chu Gedaliah chapa, Gedaliah chu Amariah chapa, Amariah chu Hezekiah chapa ahi. \x + \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Lengte 22:1—23:30; 2 Thusimbu 34:1—35:27\x*  
\v 2 “Keiman leiset chung’a thil ijakai katheh ngimhel ding ahi”, tin Pakaiyin aseiye.  
\v 3 “Keiman mihem leh gancha katheh ngim ding, chung’a leng vacha ho katheh ngim ding, Twikhanglen’a nga ho jong katheh ngim ding ahi. Migilou jouse abong abaija kalha-a, kaset tup ding, leiset chung’a mihimte kasuhgam ding ahi”, tin Pakaiyin aseiye.  
\v 4 “Keiman kakhut tah’a Judah gam le Jerusalem kasugep ding, chuleh Ba’al doi hou ho jouse, anunung pen geija ka suhgam ding ahi. Keiman milim doi houna thempu ho jouse jong, koiman ageldohkit tahlou ding’a, ka suhmang ding ahi.”  
\v 5 Ajeh chu ama hon, inting vum’a nisa, lhathah chuleh ahsi ho ahouvun, abohkhup jiuvin ahi. Amaho Pakai nung juiyin akiseijun, ahinlah amaho chu Molech Pathen hou joh ahiuve.  
\v 6 Pakai nung ajui nauva kon’a nungjam kit ho, Pakai jong hol talouva chuleh dong talou ho chu, ka suhmang soh hel ding ahi.” tin Pakaiyin aseiye.  
\v 7 Hatchungnung Pakai angsung’a thipkhen in um'in, ajeh chu tijat umtah Pakai thutanna nikho chu anaitai. Pakaiyin amite asutu in, kilhaina gantha ding jong agong’e, chuleh aman amiho jong athensotai.  
\v 8 “Hiche thutanna nikho chuleh, keiman Judah pipuho leh leng chapa te ho talen kamatsah ding, chuleh milim doihouna a chon ho jouse jong, abon’a talen kapeh ding ahi” tin Pakaiyin aseiye.  
\v 9 Henge, milim doihouna kin’a gapang tapou abon’a gotna kapeh ding, chuleh apupa insung dim’a um’a, pumhat leh duha-a thilbol ho jouse, abon’uva talen kamat sah ding ahi.   
\p
\v 10 “Hiche nikho niteng chuleh”,  
\p Pakaiyin aseiyin, “Nga kelkot a pat ka ogin kija ding chule khopi ningli jousea kithong soh ding ahi.”   
\p
\v 11 Keithela touho lunghem in kap’un, ajeh chu kivei mi ho le sumkol vei mi ho kisumang ding ahi.  
\v 12 “Meisal kadet’a Jerusalem khopi thimlai jouse kakhol chil ding, chonset muthim noiya touva, Pakaiyin thilse hihen thilpha hileh boldeh ponte, tia sei ho gotna kapeh ding ahi.  
\v 13 Anei agou jouseu kichomdoh jou keiding;  
\p A in jouseu ahom keuva kijam soh ding ahi.  
\p In thah sa jonguleh, chen thei dehlou diu;  
\p Lengpilei lhou jonglehu, lengpitwi adonlou diu ahi.   
\p
\v 14 “Tijat umtah Pakai nikho chu ahung naiye.  
\p Genthei lilhon kana nikho,  
\p Pasal thahat tah jeng jong kana nikho,  
\p Hunglhung vah ding ahi.   
\p
\v 15 Hiche nikho, Pakai lungsat kibuhlhah nikho chu – Genthei leh hesoh nasat nikho,  
\p Manthah leh ahomkeova um nikho,  
\p Muthim leh lunkham lungjin nikho,  
\p Muthim lhangkhal le meibol jin nikho,   
\p
\v 16 Gal lhangsapna le sumkon kimut nikho,  
\p Khopi pal kinokhum leh gal nasatah a kisatna nikho hi ding ahi!   
\p
\v 17 Pakai dounaa na chonset jeh uva,  
\p Mitcho banga kakimaile sah diu,  
\p Na thisan’u leivui lah a kasunlhah ding,  
\p Chuleh natahsau tol'a among dinga kijam ding ahi.   
\p
\v 18 Pakai lungsat kibuhlhah nikho tengleh na sanauva jong na dangkauva jong na kihuhhing jou lou diu ahi. Pakai lungsat chun leiset jeng jong avallhun jeng ding ahi.  
\p Aman leiset chung mijouse asuhmanga asuhbeihel ding ahi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Israel Kimvel’a Um Namdang Ho Chunga Thutanna  
\p
\v 1 Kikhou khom’un nabon’un, kikhomsohkeijun, nangho jum leh ja helou nam mite.   
\p
\v 2 Pakai thutanna nangchunguva alhum masangin, kikhom’un, Hui a changvai kisep mang banga na kisep mang kah in, kisih’un, Pakai lunghanna meikong banga aki buhlhah masang, chuleh Pakai lungset gimnei tah ahunglhun masangin, kisihun.  
\v 3 Gamsunga mi noinungten Pakai jeng hol’un, chuleh athupeh nit’un. Adih jeng’a thil bolding gouvin, chuleh nunem tah in hinkho mangun. Chutileh Pakaiyin, alunghan nikho’a na seldoh’uva chuleh sumang louva na huhdoh theiju ahi.  
\v 4 Ajeh chu Gaza leh Ashkelon khopi jong ahomkeuva kidalha ding, chule Ashdod leh Ekron khopi jong kisuchim’a kidel jamdiu ahi. \x + \xo 2:4 \xt Isa 14:29-31; Jeremiah 47:1-7; Ezekiel 25:15-17; Joel 3:4-8; Amos 1:6-8; Zechariah 9:5-7\x*   
\p
\v 5 Ada nahiuve! Nangho twikhanglen panga cheng Philistine mite, chuleh Canan gamsunga cheng ho jouse jong, hiche thutanna hi nangho chunga chuding ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiyin nangho nabeikei kah’uva na suhgam dingu ahi.  
\v 6 Philistine gam, twikhanglen pang ho, hamhing gamlah naso ding, chuleh kelngoi chingho pansatna leh ganchate kikholkhomna mun hi ding ahi.  
\v 7 Judah mi ahingdoh amoh chengsen, hiche mun hi, kineh holna a aneidiu. Janteng Ashkelon a ingem ho’a jan choldo diu ahi. Chutah leh, Pakai a Pathen’u chun, khotona neitah a amite ahinvil ding chuleh asemphat kit’a hamphatna apeh ding ahi.  
\v 8 “Keiman Moab mite ham hoithona kajan, chuleh Ammon mite ajumso nau kajai. Ama hon kamite noise tah’a anuisat’uva chuleh isahlou tah’a gal abolden’u kamu tai. \x + \xo 2:8 \xt Isa 15:1—16:14; 25:10-12; Jeremiah 48:1-47; Ezekiel 25:8-11; Amos 1:13-15; \xt Jeremiah 49:1-6; Ezekiel 21:28-32; 25:1-7; Amos 1:13-15\x*  
\v 9 “Tun, keima ka hingjing ’e,” tin Israel Pathen, thaneitah Pakai chun aseiye. “Moab leh Ammon mite kisugam ding, Sodom leh Gomorah banga kisumang soh hel ding ahi. Agamsungu jong ling le khao dimset, chikhuh jeng hi ding, chuleh a-itih’a ahomkeova kijam ding ahi.” Chuleh kamite ahingdoh chengsen, amaho adelmang’uva agam sungu achenden diu ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 2:9 \xt Semtilbu 19:24\x*  
\v 10 ama hon akiletsah ga akisan diu ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon Pathen mite chu noise tah’a atot thang’uva, thaneipen Pathen douna abol’u ahi.  
\v 11 Pakaiyin agamsung uva leiset Pathen umho jouse asuhmang ding, chutah leh amaho tija tah’a alha ding ahi. Chuteng namtin vaipin ama cheh gamsung a, Pakai Pathen chu bohkhupa ahoudiu ahi.  
\v 12 “Vo, Ethiopia mite nangho jong ka chemjam’a na lousoh hel diu ahi” tin Pakaiyin aseiye. \x + \xo 2:12 \xt Isa 18:1-7\x*  
\v 13 Chuleh Pakaiyin sahlam gamho douna-a akhut tum alapding Assyria gam asuhmang peh ding ahi. Nineveh khopi jong ahomkeuva aumsah ding, panna bei nelphai gammgo banga akoi ding ahi. \x + \xo 2:13 \xt Isa 10:5-34; 14:24-27; Nahum 1:1—3:19\x*  
\v 14 Akiletsah piu khopi chu, bongte le kelngoite kivahna leh kolna hi ding, chuleh gamsa jouse jong kol diu ahi. In-gemsa ho lah a chu, sumbupi ho, saphute, chuleh muthong ho hung cheng diu, aham gin’u kholai sung kithong ding ahi. Cedar thing a kisa in jouse jong ki suchim gam ding, chuleh in kot ho jong thilse ho kinot dim gam ding ahi.  
\v 15 Hiche khopi chu ahi, kiletsah tah’a “Keima bou alenpen kahi” tia ama kichoi sang’a, kulpi detpen’a ana um chu. Ahinlah, tunvang ahomkeuva kijam ahitan, gamlah gamsate chenna mun ahitai. Avahle ajotpa jousen, akhut tum ajeldenun, nuijat nopnan aneitauvin ahi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Jerusalem Khopi Thutanna  
\p
\v 1 Hesoh gentheina kiboldoh jing, Ohe! ada ahi! Doumah mah bol’a kisuboh soh hel, Vo! Jerusalem khopi, kimatna khopi.  
\v 2 Hiche khopi hin kisuhdihna him him adoudal in, koima thudih sei ging aumpoi. Ama hon Pakai chu atahsan pouvin chuleh ama Pathen’u kom jong anaideh pouve.  
\v 3 Khopi sung vaipo’a pangho chu, Sakei bahkai bangin kitumlet lutin, aneh ding bou akihol’un.  
\p A Thutan vaihom ho jong, kamkei hon, gilkei keija nilhah ngah’a, jan muthim lah a neh ding kihol’a, jingkah teng neh moh ima khenlouva umho tobang ahiuve.   
\p
\v 4 A themgao ho jong , jouleh nal’a ama phatchomna ding kihol ngen ahiuve. Chuleh Thempua pangho jong , Pathen thupeh nitlouvin, Hou-In sung asuboh gam tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Ahivangin, Pakaiyin khopi sung adalha pon, aumpi jingin, chuleh amaho din ima setna abolpoi. Aniseh in, aman thudih chu aphongdoh jingin, chuleh aman ima bolkhel anei poi. Amavang, thudih louva chonpa chem jum le ja lam ahepoi.  
\v 6 “Keiman nampi vaipi katheh ngim in, akisel nau kulpi bang le in ho jon ahomkeuvin kakoi tai, kholai dung ajong koima avahle aumpon, athip gamtai. Ajeh chu ahing doh amoh khat jong umlou ahi tauve.  
\v 7 Keiman kagel chu, tunvang hiche te hin eijabol intin, eiging tauvinte, kati. Ka hilchehna ho jong sang tei tauvinte, kati.Chuteng keiman achung uva jepna pehkit dang’e, chuleh achennau inho jong kisuhmang kit dahen, kati. Ahivangin, amaho jingpitah In athouvun, abolngaiju setna jeng abolun, akhoh cheh cheh jingin ahi.”   
\s1 Lhatdoh Amoh Chengse  
\p
\v 8 Pakaiyin aseiye,” Hijeh chun khongai jin, ngahhat in, keiman hiche namtin vaipi gitlou bolte ho hi, keima kadin’a, themmo kachan sah ding ahi. Ajeh chu leiset chunga lenggam ho kasuhkhom ding, achung uva ka lunghanna khosetah meikong tobang chu kabuh khum ding ahiuve. Hiche ka lunghanna meikong chun leiset pumpi ahalvam ding ahi.   
\p
\v 9 Chutengleh keiman namtin vaipi kamcheng ka sutheng’n kakhel peh ding, chute leh mitin in lung kitoh’a Pakai ahou cheh ding ahi.  
\v 10 Chutengleh, Ethiopia vadung gal‘a umho, chehsa kamiten jong, thilto ahin choi uva apeh dingu ahi.  
\v 11 Hiche nikho chuleh, nangman jum le ja nathuh tah louding, ajeh chu keima douva napantah louding ahi. Keiman nalah uva kon’a mi kiletsah ho chuleh ama kichoisang ho ka paidoh ding ahi. Chuteng kalhang theng’a chu kiletsah hoithona um talou ding ahi.  
\v 12 Ahingdoh amoh chengse, amaho chu, abon’a mi lungneng leh mi kinem sah ho jeng ahi tauve. Ajeh chu amaho chu Pakai min’a taojing ho ahiuve.  
\v 13 Akidalha Israel amoh chengsen, adihlou abolkit tahlou ding’u, jou leh nal’a jong khat le khat kilhem talou ding ahiuve. Ajeh chu, amaho chu, koiman akichatsah tah lou dingu chuleh lungmong’a, nomsel’a aneh uva chuleh kichol diu ahitai. \x + \xo 3:13 \xt Rev 14:5\x*  
\v 14 Vo, Zion chanu, O thongin la sauvin; Vo Israel kholhang sam in! Nalungthim pumpin kipah le thanom in um'in, Vo Jerusalem chanu!  
\v 15 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin akhut’a na chungthu atan ding chu alamang tan, chuleh na melma te jouse jong anomang soh tai. Pakai ama tah Israel leng ahin, nalah uva aching jing e. Nangman navel’a thilse nagin kit tahlou ding chuleh na gentheina jouse beisoh ding ahitai.  
\v 16 Hiche nikho chuleh, Jerusalem kiseipeh ding cu, “Vo, Zion, kipah thanom in, kicha hih in, natha jong lhahsam sah hih in!  
\v 17 Ajeh chu, na lailung uva Pakai na Pathen chu aching jingin, ama chu thaneitah huhingpu ahi. Aman thanom tah’a nakipapi ding, ami lungsetna chun na lungmon sah ding, nang dinga kipah thanom’a chuleh kipa la asah ding ahi.  
\v 18 “Keiman nangho, kut nikho’a lunghem leh lhasa umho jouse, kakhop khom soh ding, chuleh nangho avel’a koiman nabolset kit tahlou dingu ahi.  
\v 19 Chuleh keiman nangho bol genthei ja pangho chu nasatah’a ka bolgim ding ahi.  
\p Keiman alhasam ho leh bel ding neilou ho  
\p jouse kahuhdoh ding, chuleh muntin’a ana  
\p kidel magho, keiman kahin puikhom ding  
\p ahi. Keiman amaho chu, loupina leh minthana akpeh ding, amaho dinga ajumnao leh ajachat nau jouse chu kilamang ding ahi.   
\p
\v 20 Hiche nikho chuleh, keiman nangho jouse ka khopkhom ding, inlam’a ka puilut kitding nahiuve. Keiman nangho, leiset chung namtin vaipi lah a, minphatna leh minthanna kapeh ding, chuleh amitmu cheng uva Hamphatna kapeh ding nahiuve. Hiche hi, keima Pakai Pathen'in ka seidoh ahitai.   